Mental training methods are helpful strategies for becoming more balanced.  These include:

**Thought stopping:**  
No self-defeating thoughts, such as: &quot;I'll never make it.&quot;

**Affirmations (affirmation exercises):**  
&quot;Today, it will work!&quot; 

**Positive phrasing of sentences:**
**Not**&quot;Today, I will not be nervous at the meeting&quot;** but**&quot;I will be completely focused during the meeting. I have prepared well!&quot;

More information can be found <a href='http://www.rechance.eu/uploaded/Gelassen%20und%20sicher%20im%20Umgang%20mit%20Stress.pdf' target='_blank'>here.</a>
